Las Vegas Strip Map A Tourist's Las Vegas Strip Map 
Our Las Vegas Strip map is not a map of strip joints in Sin City, but it does shows hotels, casinos and sights along "The Strip," properly known as Las Vegas Boulevard. 
Our Las Vegas Strip map shows the hotels, casinos and sights. This Las Vegas Strip map will help you get oriented, and it shows where you can catch a monorail if your feet tire out. You can use the Las Vegas strip map to plan your day, and print the Las Vegas Strip map out to take with you.
